## Eligible Users

You are eligible to use the Software under this license if you are:

1. an individual using the Software on your own behalf;
2. a nonprofit organization, educational institution, public research
   organization, or government institution; or
3. a for-profit organization that, together with its Affiliates, has both:
   - no more than 1,000,000 USD in Gross Revenue for its most recently
     completed fiscal year; and
   - no more than 2,000,000 USD in aggregate Funding Raised.

An individual using the Software on behalf of an organization is eligible only
if that organization is eligible.

